<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>뉴스룸 클론</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <div class="logo">우아한형제들</div>
  <nav>
    <ul class="nav">
      <li>뉴스룸</li>
      <li>우아한스토리</li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>

<main class="container">

  <h1 class="title">뉴스룸</h1>

  <ul class="tabs">
    <li class="active">리포트</li>
    <li>보도자료</li>
  </ul>

  <section class="cards">

    <!-- 카드 반복 -->
    <article class="card">
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h2>우아한형제들 리포트 제목</h2>
      <p>2026.03.28</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h2>데이터로 보는 배달 트렌드</h2>
      <p>2026.03.20</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h2>외식 산업 리포트</h2>
      <p>2026.03.15</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h2>소비 패턴 변화 분석</h2>
      <p>2026.03.10</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h2>배달 플랫폼 시장 동향</h2>
      <p>2026.03.01</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h2>유저 행동 데이터 리포트</h2>
      <p>2026.02.25</p>
    </article>

  </section>

</main>

<footer class="footer">
  <p>© 우아한형제들</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
